title.rendered: TTE FM collaborates with Dubai Municipality

content.rendered: As part of TTE Facilities Management’s commitment to our city and the environment, we collaborated with Dubai Municipality to make a positive impact while promoting a culture of cleanliness and environmental responsibility. Our contribution to the initiative – “An hour with the cleaner” was focused around the lakes of the Al Qudra district in Dubai. A special thank you to Dubai Municipality for their collaboration and commitment to creating a cleaner, more sustainable Dubai. Together, we are turning a vision of cleanliness into a reality.
